The proxy behavior is as expected from the finding: `safeTransferFrom` uses the nominal amount, fees are accrued on that nominal amount, approval is raised to the nominal post-fee amount, and only total proxy spend is checked. I didn’t find `test/ExploitPOC.t.sol` in the current directory tree yet, so I’m locating the test file next to see whether the harness expects validation only or a hard profit threshold on the fork.
